Class Fulfillment

java.lang.Object
  model.SavableToService
      model.Fulfillment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Fulfillment
extends SavableToService
implements Serializable

This class acts as an object blueprint for a submission of requirements to the task author.

  • Photo
  • Text
  • Audio
  • UserdeviceId, a unique id for each android device designed to track who is the author of a task
This class is SaveableToService which means it can be encoded/decoded via String to the webservice.

zturchan
